Sentence: These superconductors are mainly classified into three structural types: (a) the hex- agonal Fe 2 P-type (or ZrNiAl-type) , (b) the orthor- hombic Co 2 P-type (or TiNiSi-type) , and (c) the orthorhombic TiFeSi-type .
In summary, we have synthesized samples of ScRuSi by an arc-melting method, and their transport properties as well as the structural phase transition are reported.
